      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a second that he isn't there, and then it hits me all over again. the house feels like it's empty, even when i'm in it. i don't even know why i bother getting out of bed anymore. what's the point of just... existing in this silence?",
